      "code": "# search quran entries containing tokens\ndef search_quran(q):\n    qn=normalize_ar(q)\n    hits=[]\n    for rec in qdata:\n        t=rec['ayah_text']\n        tn=normalize_ar(t)\n        if qn in tn or tn in qn:\n            hits.append(rec)\n    return hits\n\nhits=search_quran(query_full)\nlen(hits)",
